      "raw_text": "The Spokane district representa-\ntives-elect to the Legislature visited\nthe State Normal school at Cheney\nyesterday and decided to work for an\nappropriation of $111,130 for the\nschool for the coming year. Forty\nthousand dollars of this amount is\nneeded for a new annex\n\n\nToday the representatives are visit\ning the asylum at Medical Lake."
